data.description: Seller offering $7500 allowance on buyer’s choice with acceptable offer! This home offers wide open living spaces!  Everyone has their own space. Starting with a lovely spacious entry opened into both formal Living and Dining Rms, updated current look of wood and wrought iron railing, generous main floor Family Rm PLUS an extra roomy Family Rm in LL! New Stainless Appl, Breakfast Area in Kit surrounded by Windows bringing in bright morning sun.  Oversized Master Suite is a true surprise as is the Mstr Bath designed with individual vanities, jetted tub and walk in shower.  Expansive LL Family Rm is sure to please the kids, guests or just you enjoying video gaming or the latest Netflix Series! Not to forget the added convenience of the Wet Bar.  The huge deck facing east offers a cooler summer afternoon and also an enjoyable evening cookout plus added bonus of comfy shaded screened porch. Don't sleep on this one!  Updates: Refrig, DW Stovetop '23, both Furn Units ‘23 Carpet '21, Light Fixtures, Int Painted , Ext Painted
